{"tid":6492,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［美劇］驅魔人討論區","createTime":"2016-11-27T11:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T17:46:30.000Z","uid":30100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e06075ce47405754ef73eb989a50318e356c480","tid":6492,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人講？<br />\n<br />\nFOX將經典電影驅魔人搬上小屏幕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqg4nk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdqg4nk.jpg&h=1bc991ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《大法師電視版》(The Exorcist)，《大法師》原本是1971年William Blatty撰寫的經典恐怖小說，兩年後被拍成一部經典恐怖電影，故事描述一個有豐富驅魔經驗的老者幫助一個幾近絕望的母親驅除其行為怪異的女兒體內的惡魔。在該片大獲好評40年之後，Fox決定將其翻拍成電視劇集。Fox的新版《驅魔人》由年輕的電影編劇Jeremy Slater撰寫，被稱作「刺激的」心裡驚悚連續劇、「現代改編版」。故事描述兩個性格截然不同的男人共同幫助一個家庭驅除可怕的惡魔，讓被附體的無辜者早日康復。在此過程中，他們將面對「真正的邪惡」。"},{"pid":"3452eb7425a8974c462234544a589934c92cb383","tid":6492,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"屌你，好似好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabba57ab9d6b5701edea8d79ed2a4605a0248cb","tid":6492,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9556cc282998de31af2d3422af442eb3707ae086","tid":6492,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你，好似好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇電影版咁恐怖<br />\n但好緊張好刺激<br />\nBtw push"},{"pid":"60be9055c61045e17ff4ec8cea9a295ebabab9c0","tid":6492,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"睇過一集，覺得電影感好重，但節奏太慢唔啱feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb4431051ca39048ea9a5db7a6cac76c6d6a8b0","tid":6492,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過一集，覺得電影感好重，但節奏太慢唔啱feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初頭以為1集做1個驅魔點知6-7集都係做得1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n節奏真係慢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6776954b71366058986679c3e3267115fe2e959f","tid":6492,"uid":27057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"Father Marcus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8da91ffb3686b6e1f8145774ed8f0634d8dfea","tid":6492,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"條女好索"},{"pid":"75f35314be7ae73b162c9701756e9c13a5bdb8bb","tid":6492,"uid":18044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美劇"},{"pid":"37aa5e6f82978940d47596aa7cb92d671a9fed2b","tid":6492,"uid":2312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"最尾魔鬼上左啊媽身果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8c8c39f5